#17100
Name:	Outside a Dojo (Mitsuhama Computer Technologies)
Keywords:	mitsuhama
Description:$
As you pass through the doors of the Mitsuhama Towers you enter a beautiful
japanese garden. The sky above is blue and cloudless and all the tree's are in
bloom, a delightful scent tickling your nose. The sound of flowing water draws
your attention to the small pond, filled with fish. People in traditional
japanese dress mill around, watching you closely. A large dojo takes up the
majority of the garden, the entrance to the lobby flanked by two very large
stone samurai. A small man is standing behind a stall, repeating the same
motion of waving his hands over and over. 
~
