#17101
Name:	Before A Stall
Keywords:	stall small man
Description:$
The stall before you is plastered in Mitsuhama merchandise, more than would
seem possible to fit onto its small frame. From cyberdecks, to programs, even
commerical electronics line the deck of the stall and hang from the room. The
man behind continues waving his arms, beckoning you in to take a closer look
at what he has on offer. 
~
