#17102
Name:	The Lobby of the Dojo
Keywords:	lobby inside dojo
Description:$
You step past the stone statues in the lobby of the Dojo. Tatami mats cover
the floor and the walls are made of wood. A very attractive japanese lady
stands at the door greeting all the icons as they walk in, many of them
stopping to sign a guestbook positioned on a pedastal to the lady's left. A
Large open arch leads the way into the main room, and a smaller sliding door
leads to whereabouts as yet unknown. The amount of people who pass through
here is incredible, this must be one of the main access hosts in the complex.
~
