#17103
Name:	The Dojo Floor
Keywords:	dojo floor arch open
Description:$
Tatami mats line the floor of the dojo, cushioning your feet. Weapons line the
wall, a sign this room is meant for training between the dojo's occupants.
Icons travel through here faster than you can keep track of, often followed by
datastreams of various sizes. Fully armoured samurais watch from the corners
of the room, making sure no one tries anything they shouldn't. An archway
returns to the lobby, and a set of doors open up infront of you. The light
smell of cooking soup wafts in from the kitchen and the sound of discussion
and laughter approach from a lounge room on the opposite side of the dojo. 
~
