#17104
Name:	A Kitchen (R&D Department)
Keywords:	kitchen research and development
Description:$
The smell of freshly cooked soup and the sound of chopping fills the air as
you walk into the kitchen at the dojo. Twenty odd cooks, dressed in
traditional japanese outfits and wearing aprons, constantly prepare
ingrediants and drop them into a cooking pot. A large recipe book sits on a
heavy wooden table in the middle of the room, the cooks often leafing through
it before continuing their preperation. 
~
