#17108
Name:	A Busy Lounge
Keywords:	lounge busy laughter
Description:$
The size of this lounge takes you by suprise, as small as it looks from
outside, once inside continues as far as the eye can see in all directions.
Many people in traditional japanese garb, presumably Mitsuhama employees, sit
cross-legged at cut off tables, pondering over identical games of mahjong.
Occasionally they will move a piece, writing down something on a scroll beside
the pieces. As far as you move through this host, the door to the main dojo is
always one step behind. 
~
